{"article_id":"Zr44B2RAxNFGhKgl","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump suggested Monday","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that `` rogue killers '' could be responsible for a Saudi journalist 's disappearance","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"after a personal phone call","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"in which Trump said","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"Saudi Arabia 's King Salman strongly denied","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"any knowledge","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"of what happened to Jamal Khashoggi .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Trump also announced","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"he 'd dispatched Secretary of State Mike Pompeo to the Kingdom","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"- and anywhere else necessary -","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"to get to the bottom of the suspected murder of Khashoggi ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"who has n't been seen","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"since entering the Saudi consulate in Istanbul two weeks ago .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"The U.S. president is under growing pressure to take action on the suspected murder of the Saudi writer ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"who has been living and working in the United States ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"including contributing to The Washington Post and writing columns critical of Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Turkish officials say","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"they believe","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Saudi agents killed and dismembered Khashoggi","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"and Turkey has audio and video recordings of it .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"The crown prince , ambitious , aggressive and just 33 in a kingdom","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"long ruled by aging monarchs ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"has considerable weight in Saudi government actions .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"He and Trump 's son-in-law and senior adviser , Jared Kushner , have forged close ties .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Trump said Monday","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"he had spent about 20 minutes on the phone with King Salman , the crown prince 's 82-year-old father ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"who denied","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"having any information","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"about what had happened to Khashoggi .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"`` The king firmly denied any knowledge of it , ''","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Trump told reporters","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"as he left the White House for a trip","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"to survey hurricane damage in Florida and in Georgia .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Trump said","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"he did n't `` want to get into ( Salman 's ) mind , ''","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"but told reporters :","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"`` it sounded to me like maybe these could have been rogue killers .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"I mean ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"who knows ?","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"We 're going to try getting to the bottom of it very soon ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"but his was a flat denial . ''","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"State Department spokeswoman Heather Nauert said","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"Trump called Pompeo Sunday evening","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"and asked him to meet face-to-face with Saudi leaders .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"In Istanbul , meanwhile , investigators entered the consulate .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Turkish officials said","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"a joint probe was to be conducted by both Turkey and Saudi Arabia ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"but the makeup of the team was not immediately clear .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"The members arrived by unmarked police cars","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"but said nothing to journalists","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"waiting outside","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"as they entered the building .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"The kingdom has called the allegations of foul play `` baseless ''","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"but has offered no evidence","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"the writer left the consulate .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Trump tweeted early Monday","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"that Salman denied any knowledge of `` whatever may have happened 'to our Saudi Arabian citizen . ' '' He made that point again and again","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"as he left the White House ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"telling reporters ,","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"`` All","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"I can do","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"is report what he told me . ''","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"`` His denial to me could not have been stronger , ''","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"echoing language","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"he has used","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"to describe Russian President Vladimir Putin 's denials of meddling in the 2016 election","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"that sent Trump to the White House .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"U.S. intelligence officials have reported","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"they are certain","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"the interference took place in an effort","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"to hurt Hillary Clinton 's campaign .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Trump promised `` severe punishment '' for whoever was to blame in a `` 60 Minutes '' interview","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"that aired Sunday .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"But he has said repeatedly","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"that he does not want to halt a proposed $ 110 billion arms sale to Saudi Arabia","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"- as some in Congress have said","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"he should -","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"because it would harm the U.S. economically ..","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"Saudi Arabia has pledged to retaliate economically for any U.S. punitive action .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"`` The world is watching ,","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"the world is talking .","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"This is very important to get to the bottom of it , ''","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"Trump said .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"he understands that very well . ''","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin still plans to attend a previously scheduled Saudi conference this week","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"to address terrorist financing ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"but those plans could change","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"as the investigation progresses ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"said White House economic adviser Larry Kudlow .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"Sens . Marco Rubio and Jeff Flake , members of the Foreign Relations Committee , have said","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"Congress is prepared to move quickly and firmly","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"if Trump fails to adequately respond to Khashoggi 's disappearance .","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"Rubio said Sunday","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"that U.S.-Saudi relations may need to be `` completely revised . ''","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"`` There 's not enough money in the world for us to buy back our credibility on human rights","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"if we do not move forward","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"and take swift action , ''","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Rubio said on CBS","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"' `` Face the Nation . ''","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"More than 20 Republican and Democratic senators instructed Trump last week to order an investigation into Khashoggi 's disappearance under legislation","depth":3},{"id":102,"text":"that authorizes sanctions for perpetrators of extrajudicial killings , torture or other gross human rights violations .","depth":3},{"id":103,"text":"Khashoggi had been living in self-exile in Virginia for the past year .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":207,"left":204,"right":206,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":158,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":127,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"p